title: Windows 8.1 Professional VL Update Multilanguage - Volume Untouc
description:
Windows 8.1 Pro is built for small and medium sized businesses and delivers new levels of mobility and security, without sacrificing performance or choice, while simplifying technology. Windows 8.1 Pro provides enhanced features that help to easily connect to company networks, use devices as kiosks, encrypt data, and more.

Windows 8.1 Pro K is the Korean language version built for small and medium sized businesses and delivers new levels of mobility and security, without sacrificing performance or choice, while simplifying technology. Windows 8.1 Pro K provides enhanced features that help to easily connect to company networks, use devices as kiosks, encrypt data, and more. Windows Pro 8.1 K includes the same functionality as Windows 8.1 Pro as well as download links offering third party instant messaging and media player options.

Windows 8.1 Pro KN is the Korean language version built for small and medium sized businesses and delivers new levels of mobility and security, without sacrificing performance or choice, while simplifying technology. Windows 8.1 Pro KN provides enhanced features that help to easily connect to company networks, use devices as kiosks, encrypt data, and more. Windows Pro 8.1 KN includes the same functionality as Windows 8.1 Pro, except that it does not include certain media related technologies (Windows Media Player, Camera, Music, Video) and does not include certain apps (Mail, Calendar, Messaging, and People).

Windows 8.1 Pro N is built for small and medium sized businesses and delivers new levels of mobility and security, without sacrificing performance or choice, while simplifying technology. Windows 8.1 Pro N provides enhanced features that help to easily connect to company networks, use devices as kiosks, encrypt data, and more. Windows 8.1 Pro N includes the same functionality as Windows 8.1 Pro, except that it does not include certain media related technologies (Windows Media Player, Camera, Music, Video).
